<item>
            <title>[MJAVADOC-82] &apos;sourcepath&apos; should not be mandatory when using &apos;subpackages&apos; configuration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-82</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is impossible to use &apos;subpackages&apos; configuration without specifying &apos;sourcepath&apos; directory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This works :      &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;sourcepath&amp;gt;${basedir}/src/main/java&amp;lt;/sourcepath&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            my.package:my.package2&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;/subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but this one doesn&apos;t works (without sourcepath with sources default path)&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            my.package:my.package2&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;/subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
