                            <comment id="14438771" author="dlecan" created="Fri, 13 Oct 2006 09:31:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem still happens.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This works :&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;2.1&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;sourcepath&amp;gt;${basedir}/src/main/java&amp;lt;/sourcepath&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            my.package:my.package2&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;/subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This doesn&apos;t works :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;      &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;2.1&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            my.package:my.package2&lt;br/&gt;
          &amp;lt;/subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;	  &lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Embedded error: Error rendering Maven report: Exit code: 1 - javadoc: error - No packages or classes specified.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14438819" author="siveton" created="Sat, 14 Oct 2006 07:31:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried it on dummy projects (see file) with jdk 1.4&amp;amp;1.5 and all seems to work.&lt;br/&gt;
Could you send us a true project?&lt;br/&gt;
Also, could you tried with -Ddebug=true and verify the content of &apos;options&apos; and &apos;package-list&apos; files in target\site\apidocs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let me know.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14438721" author="dlecan" created="Mon, 16 Oct 2006 03:30:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have found why I doesn&apos;t work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My pom declares two uses of maven-javadoc-plugin :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1 in &amp;lt;build&amp;gt; section&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1 in &amp;lt;reporting&amp;gt; section&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The first one was empty (no configuration) :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/plugin&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The second one declared the real configuration :&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;reporting&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;2.1&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
my.package:my.package2&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/subpackages&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems to be related to MNG-1857 or MNG-1931.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;m sorry, I think you can fix and close this issue&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14438782" author="siveton" created="Mon, 16 Oct 2006 06:09:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closed as suggested. &lt;br/&gt;
Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
